// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - MM_Hero_SL8-9_Task_01 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page DocIntro Text :
"P2661815841" "Before I dispatch you as the honorless dog you are, I must know why you have taken such cowardly actions.  Why do you attack your own enforcers of law?"
// Answer Text :
"P2730955059" "I have done no such thing..."
// Answer Text :
"P4060782435" "Leave"
// Page DocIntroMurders Text :
"P4216998529" "And even now you lie.  You not only shame yourself, but everyone who calls you friend.  It is good that you planned on using that policeman as a hostage, or I would have suspected something different.  His lifeless body has proven that you can not be trusted by anyone."
// Answer Text :
"P1351368557" "What are you talking about? I saved the officer!"
// Page DocIntroInvestigate Text :
"P4265821505" "I am silent, not blind.  I found the body of the officer further in.  But yet... But yet I find you here.  And you did not pass by me without my knowledge.<br><br>The wounds were caused by your powers, not one of these Maltese mercenaries' crude weapons.<br><br>Something is not fitting correctly here.  How were you at two places at once?"
// Answer Text :
"P1624144502" "I'm trying to tell you.  I'm here to clear my name."
// Page DocIntroRaiders Text :
"P1089389038" "My contract is to assassinate you, and I never break my word, for my word is my honor.  Yet, my contract does not state WHEN I must kill you.  I shall allow you to clear your name.... And observe.  Do as you must, {HeroName}."
// Answer Text :
"P3137282588" "And I will."
// Page DocIntroCanIHelp Text :
"P1056325589" "How could you take my identity, you false {HeroName}!  And not only that, how could you dare brainwash me into performing these evil deeds!<br><br>If it wasn't for Silent Blade here, I would have been a goner.  Thank you for saving me, the good {HeroName}.  Now, do those dastardly deeds you villainous types do, since I am in no condition to stop you, being a heroic type and all.  The assassinating thing you do.  Now, get it over with."
// Answer Text :
"P1693326563" "But you're MY double!"
// Page DocIntroFinish Text :
"P4188873005" "Ha!  Like Silent Blade is going to believe - AAAAaaarrrggggggh....."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3514536733" "You need to clear your name at once.  It's obvious someone is trying to frame you for crimes you didn't commit.  If you don't do this now, who knows how hard it'll be to clear your name in the future.  Surely if you explain to the Police Commissioner, both of you can get to the bottom of this."
// AcceptString :
"P3192969768" "Talk with the Police Commissioner to clear your name."
// SendOffString :
"P1551088811" "In order to clear up this misunderstanding, you'll need to walk down to City Hall and turn yourself over to the Commissioner.  From there, you two can discuss what this is all about."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2258161222" "Turn yourself over to the police to clear your name."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2137916211" "You still need to turn yourself over to the Police Commissioner."
// TaskTitle :
"P2179378759" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Unusual Suspect</color></span></scale></font>"
// TaskSubTitle :
"P1399212272" "<span align=center><color orange><i>Hero Morality Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1064803921" "What's going on here?  It looks like City Hall is under attack!"

